org.apache.spark.sql.streaming

Class SourceStatus

  • Object
    • org.apache.spark.sql.streaming.SourceStatus

  • public class SourceStatus
extends Object
    :: Experimental :: Status and metrics of a streaming Source.

    param: description Description of the source corresponding to this status. param: offsetDesc Description of the current offset if known. param: inputRate Current rate (rows/sec) at which data is being generated by the source. param: processingRate Current rate (rows/sec) at which the query is processing data from the source. param: triggerDetails Low-level details of the currently active trigger (e.g. number of rows processed in trigger, latency of intermediate steps, etc.). If no trigger is active, then it will have details of the last completed trigger.

    Since:
    2.0.0
